{"tid":826112,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【消委報告】空氣清新機表現參差　小米1099元淨化器勝5480元Dyson","createTime":"2018-09-18T04:15:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-11T11:07:35.000Z","uid":20933,"like":14,"dislike":51,"uniUserReply":73,"replies":[{"pid":"681aac479e23aefc172d242a57333e76f63018b7","tid":826112,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T04:15:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180918/s00001/2a44ff02a996e868766cf1fd59295cc0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180918%2Fs00001%2F2a44ff02a996e868766cf1fd59295cc0.jpg&h=f6ef98fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n空氣污染情況引人關注，近年不少港人會選擇購置空氣清新機。消委會近日測試12款樣本，發現其去除香煙煙霧、塵埃及花粉的速度參差，尤其在甲醛去除上表現懸殊，有一款售價1099元的空氣清新機，空氣淨化速度及整體表現較兩款逾5000元的樣本優勝。<br />\n<br />\n樣本價格介乎1099元至7080元，相差超過5倍，惟前者的小米樣本取得4分總評分，較後者的Blueair樣本多0.5分；而售價低於5000元的樣本，表現亦相對5480元至7080元的樣本較佳。<br />\n<br />\n12款空氣淨化機均隨機附有隔除香煙煙霧、塵埃等顆粒物的過濾器，以及可除臭或去除氣態污染物。潔淨空氣量（CADR）數值愈高，即其淨化該污染物的速度愈快，當中Dyson「Pure Cool Link TP03清除煙霧」的表現在全部樣本中較遜色，而飛利浦及日立樣本的除顆粒物的速度明顯較高，獲5點評分。<br />\n<br />\n在去除甲醛方面，消委會指全部樣本均可降低空氣中的甲醛濃度，速度最低和最高的樣本相差高達26倍。當中飛利浦樣本表現突出，量得除甲醛CADR達每分鐘139.9立方呎；法國特福的樣本則速度較慢，量得每分鐘5.1立方呎。報告又指，有七成半樣本除甲醛的評分，均在2.5分或以下。<br />\n<br />\n另外，消委會表示，4款聲稱適用房間面積較細的樣本，其清除顆粒物的速度較3款聲稱適面積較大的樣本為高；提醒產品聲稱的適用面積，未必能幫助消費者評估產品的實際淨化表現，促請廠商標註產品的潔淨空氣量和採用的測試標準，以便消費者參考。"},{"pid":"1ad76e5587fb33bb273bb23582ae8fafbf8e29a4","tid":826112,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T04:15:38.000Z","msg":"牌子／型號／售價／總評分（最高五星）／空氣淨化表現（最高五星）：<br />\n<br />\n飛利浦／AC3259/31／4988元／4.5星／4.5星<br />\n<br />\n日立／EP-NZG70J／4990元／4.5星／4星<br />\n<br />\n捷家伴／PAC2302／2888元／3.5星／3星<br />\n<br />\n無印良品／MJ-AP1GL／3580元／3星／3星<br />\n<br />\nb-Mola／NCCO1702／4288元／3星／3星<br />\n<br />\n聲寶／KC-AH50-W／4430元4星／4星<br />\n<br />\nPanasonic／F-PXM55H／3480元／4星／3.5星<br />\n<br />\n小米／空氣淨化器2S(AC-M4-AA)／1099元／4星／3.5星<br />\n<br />\nBlueair／Classic 405(SmokeStop)／7080元／3.5星／3.5星<br />\n<br />\n法國特福／PU4065／2698元／3星／2.5星<br />\n<br />\nDyson／Pure Cool TP04／5480元／3星／3星<br />\n<br />\nDyson／Pure Cool Link TP03／5480元／3星／2.5星"},{"pid":"3365b025d35dab752f94bf7a6b6620b664d6e539","tid":826112,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T04:15:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180918/s00001/1537239741237\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180918%2Fs00001%2F1537239741237&d=T59rwxhmKKKIcI%2B98AzLDPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=d00a816f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180918%2Fs00001%2F1537239741237&h=deca7132\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180918/s00001/1537239741237</a>"},{"pid":"c11027efe746f8aadf5ee74ca244144a432bb29f","tid":826112,"uid":74058,"like":18,"dislike":104,"score":-86,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T04:16:39.000Z","msg":"小米不嬲好用"},{"pid":"bd4fdbfcbe7de76675139d150575dc92d011532a","tid":826112,"uid":118675,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"c11027efe746f8aadf5ee74ca244144a432bb29f","tid":826112,"uid":74058,"like":18,"dislike":104,"score":-86,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T04:16:39.000Z","msg":"小米不嬲好用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T04:19:16.000Z","msg":"耐唔耐用先？"},{"pid":"b1e1c3c9fde96778f9419a5c7c7e5498496c80b2","tid":826112,"uid":119173,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T04:20:17.000Z","msg":"呢d空氣淨化機係唔係要keep 住定期換filter/濾芯?"},{"pid":"c41d2a95e774b1f4a3137ccbee9dc201655aa0bf","tid":826112,"uid":42367,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T04:20:40.000Z","msg":"無amway？？"},{"pid":"b7396efb27bdd4ffeeb8eace5edce5735c007910","tid":826112,"uid":42815,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T04:22:39.000Z","msg":"咁要買飛利蒲同日立了"},{"pid":"b3553879b9238a9bf5632853155460e0351a6207","tid":826112,"uid":76063,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"quote":{"pid":"b7396efb27bdd4ffeeb8eace5edce5735c007910","tid":826112,"uid":42815,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T04:22:39.000Z","msg":"咁要買飛利蒲同日立了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T04:25:20.000Z","msg":"agree 因為都冇測試用耐左會唔會爆炸"},{"pid":"3a3037e125aa43bf23ee31d773277c286ad71593","tid":826112,"uid":6562,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T04:26:48.000Z","msg":"用緊果個小米2S 憎間野 純粹貪平 其他好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔覺特別好 用到 叫做OK咁囉 <br />\n睇說明書個芯好似係要年幾兩年換一次 話部機會提你換"},{"pid":"d1a29ba682d7d174509d3a71ccbb417259bd4efa","tid":826112,"uid":19501,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T04:28:41.000Z","msg":"之前話小米空氣清新機個內籠未拆包裝，個APP都顯示淨化緊空氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a334182f4c082e83c8147280c3a7643b82df11d5","tid":826112,"uid":126100,"like":0,"dislike":20,"score":-20,"quote":{"pid":"d1a29ba682d7d174509d3a71ccbb417259bd4efa","tid":826112,"uid":19501,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T04:28:41.000Z","msg":"之前話小米空氣清新機個內籠未拆包裝，個APP都顯示淨化緊空氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T04:30:19.000Z","msg":"未拆包裝都有空氣㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9a5f69d2e7902dd3396aa10dcc6428511d77b3e","tid":826112,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T04:30:19.000Z","msg":"Panasonic／F-PXM55H／3480元／4星／3.5星<br />\n<br />\n屌你空氣淨化得3.5 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1e39d257495e4bac5d92d6d20663df9e26fdc77","tid":826112,"uid":19501,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"a334182f4c082e83c8147280c3a7643b82df11d5","tid":826112,"uid":126100,"like":0,"dislike":20,"score":-20,"quote":{"pid":"d1a29ba682d7d174509d3a71ccbb417259bd4efa","tid":826112,"uid":19501,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T04:28:41.000Z","msg":"之前話小米空氣清新機個內籠未拆包裝，個APP都顯示淨化緊空氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T04:30:19.000Z","msg":"未拆包裝都有空氣㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T04:33:19.000Z","msg":"記錯，原來係濾芯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大陸霧霾成災，大陸品牌小米推出空氣清新機，售價僅699人民幣，聲稱可有效過濾99.7%的PM2.5污染物；不過有網民發現，小米空氣清新機透過手機APP顯示的空氣指數，較用儀器測出的實際指數低幾成，質疑小米造假。<br />\n<br />\n小米空氣清新機內置檢測裝置，用戶須透過手機APP，查看室內空氣指數。前日（9日），一名網民在微博發言，發現小米空氣清新機有古怪，即使濾芯的塑膠包裝未有拆除，但APP仍顯示室內空氣指數下降，又顯示濾芯已經有所消耗。網民紛紛質疑，濾芯未拆封就可以過濾空氣中的污染物？<br />\n<br />\n負責該產品的小米負責人蘇峻回應質疑，指APP顯示的濾芯消耗，是根據清新機運作的時間計數；至於空氣指數為何會下降，蘇峻則稱空氣質素會因為顆粒物沉降及局部空氣流動，發生變化。<br />\n<br />\n由於質疑廣為流傳，不少大陸科技網站都爭相「測試」小米空氣清新機的效能。一家科技網站用專業空氣檢測儀器，測試小米空氣清新機，宣稱該產品確有空氣淨化的效果，但使用的檢測裝置非常廉價，APP顯示的數據不準，而且會根據風速等作出調整，有時會出現「蒙蔽用戶」的現象。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/china/%E5%B0%8F%E7%B1%B3%E7%A9%BA%E6%B0%A3%E6%B8%85%E6%96%B0%E6%A9%9F-%E6%BF%BE%E8%8A%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8B%86%E5%B0%81%E4%BB%8D%E9%A1%AF%E7%A4%BA%E6%B1%A1%E6%9F%93%E7%89%A9%E6%B8%9B%E5%B0%91-%E9%81%AD%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E9%80%A0%E5%81%87/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%25E5%25B0%258F%25E7%25B1%25B3%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E6%25B8%2585%25E6%2596%25B0%25E6%25A9%259F-%25E6%25BF%25BE%25E8%258A%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258B%2586%25E5%25B0%2581%25E4%25BB%258D%25E9%25A1%25AF%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E6%25B1%25A1%25E6%259F%2593%25E7%2589%25A9%25E6%25B8%259B%25E5%25B0%2591-%25E9%2581%25AD%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E7%2596%2591%25E9%2580%25A0%25E5%2581%2587%2F&d=T59rwxhmKKKIcI%2B98AzLDPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=6522b9ad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%25E5%25B0%258F%25E7%25B1%25B3%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E6%25B8%2585%25E6%2596%25B0%25E6%25A9%259F-%25E6%25BF%25BE%25E8%258A%25AF%25