H10，咁緊係輸俾小米啦，小米CHEAP極都仲係H11。"},{"pid":"330037e23a896fd4c70b3f8f0aa22775ea3c3864","tid":826112,"uid":15984,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T05:10:22.000Z","msg":"Dyson 隻HEPA 撚港女同連登仔就得<br />\n啲Filtration rate 用ISO 標準出哂事"},{"pid":"e4adfe6419dd7e9e2f0ebd1f3e5a85b368b6f1a9","tid":826112,"uid":22736,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f1e39d257495e4bac5d92d6d20663df9e26fdc77","tid":826112,"uid":19501,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"a334182f4c082e83c8147280c3a7643b82df11d5","tid":826112,"uid":126100,"like":0,"dislike":20,"score":-20,"quote":{"pid":"d1a29ba682d7d174509d3a71ccbb417259bd4efa","tid":826112,"uid":19501,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T04:28:41.000Z","msg":"之前話小米空氣清新機個內籠未拆包裝，個APP都顯示淨化緊空氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T04:30:19.000Z","msg":"未拆包裝都有空氣㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T04:33:19.000Z","msg":"記錯，原來係濾芯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大陸霧霾成災，大陸品牌小米推出空氣清新機，售價僅699人民幣，聲稱可有效過濾99.7%的PM2.5污染物；不過有網民發現，小米空氣清新機透過手機APP顯示的空氣指數，較用儀器測出的實際指數低幾成，質疑小米造假。<br />\n<br />\n小米空氣清新機內置檢測裝置，用戶須透過手機APP，查看室內空氣指數。前日（9日），一名網民在微博發言，發現小米空氣清新機有古怪，即使濾芯的塑膠包裝未有拆除，但APP仍顯示室內空氣指數下降，又顯示濾芯已經有所消耗。網民紛紛質疑，濾芯未拆封就可以過濾空氣中的污染物？<br />\n<br />\n負責該產品的小米負責人蘇峻回應質疑，指APP顯示的濾芯消耗，是根據清新機運作的時間計數；至於空氣指數為何會下降，蘇峻則稱空氣質素會因為顆粒物沉降及局部空氣流動，發生變化。<br />\n<br />\n由於質疑廣為流傳，不少大陸科技網站都爭相「測試」小米空氣清新機的效能。一家科技網站用專業空氣檢測儀器，測試小米空氣清新機，宣稱該產品確有空氣淨化的效果，但使用的檢測裝置非常廉價，APP顯示的數據不準，而且會根據風速等作出調整，有時會出現「蒙蔽用戶」的現象。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/china/%E5%B0%8F%E7%B1%B3%E7%A9%BA%E6%B0%A3%E6%B8%85%E6%96%B0%E6%A9%9F-%E6%BF%BE%E8%8A%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8B%86%E5%B0%81%E4%BB%8D%E9%A1%AF%E7%A4%BA%E6%B1%A1%E6%9F%93%E7%89%A9%E6%B8%9B%E5%B0%91-%E9%81%AD%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E9%80%A0%E5%81%87/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%25E5%25B0%258F%25E7%25B1%25B3%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E6%25B8%2585%25E6%2596%25B0%25E6%25A9%259F-%25E6%25BF%25BE%25E8%258A%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258B%2586%25E5%25B0%2581%25E4%25BB%258D%25E9%25A1%25AF%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E6%25B1%25A1%25E6%259F%2593%25E7%2589%25A9%25E6%25B8%259B%25E5%25B0%2591-%25E9%2581%25AD%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E7%2596%2591%25E9%2580%25A0%25E5%2581%2587%2F&d=T59rwxhmKKKIcI%2B98AzLDPiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=6522b9ad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%25E5%25B0%258F%25E7%25B1%25B3%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E6%25B8%2585%25E6%2596%25B0%25E6%25A9%259F-%25E6%25BF%25BE%25E8%258A%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258B%2586%25E5%25B0%2581%25E4%25BB%258D%25E9%25A1%25AF%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E6%25B1%25A1%25E6%259F%2593%25E7%2589%25A9%25E6%25B8%259B%25E5%25B0%2591-%25E9%2581%25AD%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E7%2596%2591%25E9%2580%25A0%25E5%2581%2587%2F&h=3ff44f9b\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/china/%E5%B0%8F%E7%B1%B3%E7%A9%BA%E6%B0%A3%E6%B8%85%E6%96%B0%E6%A9%9F-%E6%BF%BE%E8%8A%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8B%86%E5%B0%81%E4%BB%8D%E9%A1%AF%E7%A4%BA%E6%B1%A1%E6%9F%93%E7%89%A9%E6%B8%9B%E5%B0%91-%E9%81%AD%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E9%80%A0%E5%81%87/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T05:10:23.000Z","msg":"大陸只有騙子是真的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d779828a176977cf95139e066faa1956890e91f3","tid":826112,"uid":57346,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"71d472f93287a961a16fd1a625b3b15e3f533d30","tid":826112,"uid":4917,"like":7,"dislike":5,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T04:42:56.000Z","msg":"見到小米贏都知唔使睇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T05:10:31.000Z","msg":"佢淨係贏dyson啫，標題講到好勁咁！"},{"pid":"7bb7df257af0f050bd4b7736798c3e902e0ff5f8","tid":826112,"uid":146769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T05:10:52.000Z","msg":"無事嘅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你夠膽唔怕死咪買小米"},{"pid":"e84a83745b0e3